==Dutch==

===Verb===
'''vinden'''
# To [[find]] (after searching).
#: ''Gevonden!'' &mdash; Found it!
#: ''Ik zal je vinden.'' &mdash; I'll find you.
# To [[find]]; to [[come across]].
#: ''Plots vond ik een pen.'' &mdash; All of a sudden I found a pen.
# To [[find]]; to [[think]]; to [[feel]]; to be of [[opinion]].
#: ''Ze vinden de film walgelijk.'' &mdash; They find the film disgusting.

